# star-toml-pack — required `Cargo.toml` entries

Generated by star-toml-pack from `stp:StarTomlModule`'s `stp:cargoDependency`
facts in `ontology.ttl`. Do not edit.

The generated `src/star_toml_config.rs` module does not compile without these
entries in the consumer crate's `Cargo.toml`; they are listed here (rather
than only implied) because this pack does not yet merge them into
`Cargo.toml` directly (see Consumer-effort gap in
`docs/packs/L5_VALIDATION_REPORT.md`'s star-toml-pack section).

```toml
[dependencies]
{% for d in deps %}{% if not "dev-dependency" in d.dep %}{{ d.dep }}
{% endif %}{% endfor %}

[dev-dependencies]
{% for d in deps %}{% if "dev-dependency" in d.dep %}{{ d.dep }}
{% endif %}{% endfor %}
```
